11
00:01:02,540 --> 00:01:03,340
I...

12
00:01:04,740 --> 00:01:06,660
I'm just not ready.

13
00:01:10,980 --> 00:01:12,300
As my concubine,

14
00:01:13,300 --> 00:01:15,180
you actually want to ask me to leave.

15
00:01:17,100 --> 00:01:17,820
Lady Ling,

16
00:01:18,620 --> 00:01:20,700
when you don't even know
how to compete for my favor,

17
00:01:21,820 --> 00:01:23,860
how can you keep a foothold
in the harem?

18
00:01:24,740 --> 00:01:26,340
I don't want to compete for your favor.

19
00:01:28,660 --> 00:01:30,060
Because your favor

20
00:01:30,340 --> 00:01:32,300
will only make me

21
00:01:33,380 --> 00:01:34,460
more dangerous, Your Majesty.

22
00:01:39,820 --> 00:01:40,460
Good.

23
00:01:41,660 --> 00:01:43,180
You're smarter than I think you are.

24
00:01:48,700 --> 00:01:50,220
Since you choose the other way,

25
00:01:51,300 --> 00:01:53,100
you'd better prove your worth.

26
00:02:01,820 --> 00:02:03,700
[Jiuhua Hall]
You barbarians from the Fire clan,

27
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:05,620
instead of surrendering to us,

28
00:02:05,620 --> 00:02:07,340
you actually dared to rebel against us.

29
00:02:07,620 --> 00:02:08,580
I decided

30
00:02:08,900 --> 00:02:10,540
to have all these rebels
of the Fire clan

31
00:02:11,580 --> 00:02:12,860
decapitated.

32
00:02:13,740 --> 00:02:16,420
Their heads will be hung for ten days

33
00:02:17,180 --> 00:02:18,500
as a warning to others.

34
00:02:19,580 --> 00:02:20,780
Please spare us, Your Royal Highness.

35
00:02:23,540 --> 00:02:25,500
Mother, please take back this order.

36
00:02:26,420 --> 00:02:28,420
For these humble people
from another clan,

37
00:02:28,660 --> 00:02:31,140
are you refuting me in public?

38
00:02:31,740 --> 00:02:32,460
I don't dare, Mother.

39
00:02:33,740 --> 00:02:37,020
But the late Emperor had signed
a peace treaty with the three clans.

40
00:02:37,740 --> 00:02:38,980
If we break the treaty,

41
00:02:39,740 --> 00:02:40,620
we'll be disobeying the late Emperor...

42
00:02:40,620 --> 00:02:41,940
How could the late Emperor

43
00:02:41,940 --> 00:02:43,060
have such a cowardly son like you?

44
00:02:45,940 --> 00:02:46,980
I order you

45
00:02:47,020 --> 00:02:49,660
to kill all these rebels
of the Fire clan now!

46
00:03:02,260 --> 00:03:02,980
What?

47
00:03:03,780 --> 00:03:06,380
Now, you don't even dare hold a sword?

48
00:03:07,380 --> 00:03:09,220
If I remember correctly,

49
00:03:09,700 --> 00:03:11,300
when you ascended the throne,

50
00:03:11,380 --> 00:03:12,700
you killed so many people

51
00:03:13,780 --> 00:03:15,940
without showing any mercy.

52
00:03:54,020 --> 00:03:54,780
Your Royal Highness,

53
00:03:55,100 --> 00:03:56,540
His Majesty asked me

54
00:03:56,900 --> 00:03:59,020
to prepare the top-tier tea for you.

55
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:12,820
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.

56
00:04:13,100 --> 00:04:15,140
Please follow me to get changed.

57
00:04:22,060 --> 00:04:23,740
You humble slave,

58
00:04:23,900 --> 00:04:25,780
you've had this position
only because of me.

59
00:04:26,220 --> 00:04:28,340
Now, you're an imperial concubine

60
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:31,540
and you dare play such a trick
in front of me.

61
00:04:33,220 --> 00:04:35,300
Calm down, Mother. Lady Ling is just...

62
00:04:35,620 --> 00:04:36,700
You get me wrong, Your Royal Highness.

63
00:04:40,300 --> 00:04:41,820
I can have this rich life

64
00:04:42,380 --> 00:04:43,540
all because of you, Your Royal Highness,

65
00:04:44,140 --> 00:04:45,340
not His Majesty.

66
00:04:45,780 --> 00:04:47,980
I had meant to serve tea for you
in His Majesty's place

67
00:04:48,060 --> 00:04:50,700
and break the rumor
that the two of you don't get along.

68
00:04:51,260 --> 00:04:52,300
So in front of another clan,

69
00:04:52,420 --> 00:04:54,340
it would show the impressive dignity
of our Human clan

70
00:04:54,460 --> 00:04:55,500
and frighten the other four clans.

71
00:04:55,860 --> 00:04:57,180
However, I was too rash

72
00:04:57,620 --> 00:04:59,020
to choose the best time.

73
00:05:01,380 --> 00:05:02,740
The best time?

74
00:05:03,060 --> 00:05:04,940
Looks like

75
00:05:05,420 --> 00:05:07,060
there are more smart people
in this palace.

76
00:05:07,340 --> 00:05:08,980
You flatter me, Your Royal Highness.

77
00:05:09,780 --> 00:05:10,580
Please punish me.

78
00:05:10,980 --> 00:05:12,020
You deserve to be punished.

79
00:05:12,340 --> 00:05:13,370
Lady Ling's committed
a breach of etiquette

80
00:05:13,370 --> 00:05:14,100
in front of the Emperor and me

81
00:05:14,260 --> 00:05:16,180
and should be flogged
according to the law.

82
00:05:16,380 --> 00:05:16,900
Someone coming.

83
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:23,060
Take her away.

84
00:05:23,260 --> 00:05:23,780
- Yes.
- Yes.

85
00:05:36,700 --> 00:05:37,700
Silly woman,

86
00:05:38,460 --> 00:05:40,940
is this the way
you serve as my new sword?

87
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:44,380
Saya,

88
00:05:44,860 --> 00:05:46,500
elders of our Huan clan have heard

89
00:05:46,700 --> 00:05:48,460
the Emperor of the Human clan
have a new favorite.

90
00:05:48,660 --> 00:05:50,940
I'm afraid you'll lose
your position in the harem.

91
00:05:51,500 --> 00:05:52,860
I'm in charge of the harem.

92
00:05:53,460 --> 00:05:54,300
You don't need to worry.

93
00:05:55,060 --> 00:05:56,620
Since you came here,

94
00:05:56,660 --> 00:05:58,020
you've never slept with the Emperor.

95
00:05:58,380 --> 00:06:00,180
Why do you think you're in charge?

96
00:06:01,660 --> 00:06:03,820
I have my plan
about how to deal with that slave.

97
00:06:04,100 --> 00:06:05,340
I don't need you to tell me what to do.

98
00:06:05,460 --> 00:06:07,940
You should forget that you were once
a general who fought on the battlefield,

99
00:06:08,340 --> 00:06:10,140
let go of your dignity

100
00:06:10,220 --> 00:06:12,100
and do what you're supposed to do.

101
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:20,620
[Tinghan Palace]

102
00:07:00,820 --> 00:07:01,420
Lady Ling.

103
00:07:01,740 --> 00:07:05,500
♪The stars move, the traces fade♪

104
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:06,980
Do you know what you did today

105
00:07:09,020 --> 00:07:10,300
may have got you killed?

106
00:07:12,180 --> 00:07:13,180
I do.

107
00:07:14,820 --> 00:07:16,140
But I do not regret it.

108
00:07:17,540 --> 00:07:19,060
Why did you help me out?

109
00:07:20,660 --> 00:07:21,780
I don't know

110
00:07:22,740 --> 00:07:24,660
what Your Majesty had suffered.

111
00:07:26,140 --> 00:07:27,180
But I know

112
00:07:28,380 --> 00:07:29,820
you're bearing everything now

113
00:07:30,380 --> 00:07:32,380
for your bigger success in the future.

114
00:07:32,380 --> 00:07:35,820
♪The wind sweeps,
wish I could see you in my next life♪

115
00:07:35,820 --> 00:07:37,180
How can you be so sure?

116
00:07:39,620 --> 00:07:41,220
I've never been wrong about anyone.

117
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:44,780
I've never been wrong about anyone.

118
00:07:46,020 --> 00:07:48,820
♪The stars twinkle and darken♪

119
00:07:48,820 --> 00:07:51,140
You are so like an old friend

120
00:07:51,140 --> 00:07:52,340
of mine.

121
00:07:52,660 --> 00:07:53,460
I do?

122
00:07:53,460 --> 00:07:55,260
♪The frost shakes down.
I then pick up a hallow branch♪

123
00:07:55,260 --> 00:07:56,180
What kind of old friend?

124
00:07:56,340 --> 00:07:58,100
♪If it snows, let's grow old together♪

125
00:07:58,100 --> 00:08:00,180
Someone I have
a love-hate relationship with.

126
00:08:00,180 --> 00:08:03,100
♪I once wished to be
candlelight and butterfly♪

127
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:06,220
♪That would forever flicker and fly♪

128
00:08:06,220 --> 00:08:10,340
Your Majesty, do you take me
as someone else's substitute?

129
00:08:11,100 --> 00:08:12,580
No one can be her substitute.

130
00:08:28,180 --> 00:08:34,500
♪The stars move, the traces fade♪

131
00:08:34,940 --> 00:08:40,580
♪Hold my hand.
You once did makeup for me♪

132
00:08:41,900 --> 00:08:47,220
♪Giving me love and making me fall♪

133
00:08:47,220 --> 00:08:49,340
Here is a written instruction
from Her Royal Highness.

134
00:08:55,580 --> 00:08:58,080
"As reported, some evil ones
of the Spirit clan

135
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,900
have appeared in the capital city.

136
00:09:00,460 --> 00:09:04,180
I hereby request the Emperor to send
more people to conduct a search.

137
00:09:04,500 --> 00:09:06,740
Anyone of the Spirit clan

138
00:09:06,980 --> 00:09:10,260
must be killed on the spot,
without fail."

139
00:09:11,140 --> 00:09:12,340
Please tell Her Royal Highness
to rest assured.

140
00:09:13,260 --> 00:09:15,300
I'll have them executed immediately.

141
00:09:15,860 --> 00:09:17,540
I won't let go of anyone
of the Spirit clan.

142
00:09:46,300 --> 00:09:48,140
Why is my spiritual power leaking?

143
00:10:05,700 --> 00:10:07,620
There is medicinal liquor
in the ointment?

144
00:10:15,460 --> 00:10:16,260
No.

145
00:10:16,740 --> 00:10:18,820
I can't expose myself here.

146
00:11:02,940 --> 00:11:04,500
I guessed right.

147
00:11:06,460 --> 00:11:08,460
You're of the evil Spirit clan.

148
00:11:29,050 --> 00:11:31,770
♪My eyebrows are outlined
against the rain♪

149
00:11:32,010 --> 00:11:35,510
♪Lovesickness tastes like bitter wine♪

150
00:11:36,530 --> 00:11:39,210
♪The wind signs through destiny♪

151
00:11:39,610 --> 00:11:42,850
♪Love and hate are forever gone♪

152
00:11:43,010 --> 00:11:46,650
♪Don't ask where I'm going♪

153
00:11:47,090 --> 00:11:50,290
♪I won't change my love for you♪

154
00:11:50,530 --> 00:11:54,010
♪My destination is my fate,
my obsession is to wait♪

155
00:11:54,290 --> 00:11:58,090
♪I'm just destined to wander♪

156
00:11:58,730 --> 00:12:01,770
♪If I'm always greedy♪

157
00:12:02,130 --> 00:12:05,490
♪You're what I want for this life♪

158
00:12:06,170 --> 00:12:09,210
♪Yet you don't even look back
when the song ends♪

159
00:12:09,490 --> 00:12:12,970
♪Who gets stuck in the dream with me?♪

160
00:12:12,970 --> 00:12:16,530
♪Old memories never yield♪

161
00:12:16,650 --> 00:12:20,370
♪Under the spring breeze,
the flowers bloom as before♪

162
00:12:20,570 --> 00:12:24,050
♪When clouds are dispersed,
I will disappear♪

163
00:12:24,330 --> 00:12:27,410
♪However far away I stay,
I'm always who I am♪

164
00:12:27,950 --> 00:12:32,400
♪The moonlight gently falls
into your eyes♪
